Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.96,0:00:14.97,Show Title,,0,0,0,,{\fs142.5\fnGallow Tree\blur1\pos(463.949,598.286)}KAMEN RIDER
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.28,0:00:15.87,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,Shocker is coming,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.87,0:00:19.16,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,with its armies\Nstraight from hell
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.41,0:00:23.08,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,Their black shadows\Nthreaten us all
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.08,0:00:26.71,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,but I'll fight to maintain\Nthe peace of our world!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.71,0:00:30.46,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,Go! Go! Let's go!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.46,0:00:33.63,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,With my shining machine...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.01,0:00:36.76,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,Rider Jump!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.76,0:00:40.22,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,Rider Kick!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.31,0:00:44.77,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,Kamen Rider, Kamen Rider
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.77,0:00:48.15,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,Rider, Rider!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.40,0:00:51.03,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,Rider Jump!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.11,0:00:54.61,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,Rider Kick!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.87,0:00:59.41,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,Kamen Rider, Kamen Rider
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.41,0:01:02.75,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,Rider, Rider!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.34,0:01:11.08,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Ichimonji Hayato is the Kamen\NRider, a cyborg.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.08,0:01:13.27,Narrator,,0,0,0,,He was modified by the evil\NShocker, a secret
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.27,0:01:15.18,Narrator,,0,0,0,,organization plotting\Nworld domination.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.18,0:01:18.76,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Kamen Rider has pledged to\Nfight Shocker and free humanity!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.76,0:01:23.77,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Having inherited the Kamen\NRider mantle from Hongo Takeshi,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.77,0:01:27.31,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Ichimonji Hayato has become\NJapan's newest protector.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.31,0:01:30.62,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Kamen Rider is currently locked in\Nbattle with the monstrous Sabotegron,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.62,0:01:32.91,Narrator,,0,0,0,,who was dispatched from\NShocker's Mexico Branch to Japan.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.91,0:01:36.23,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Sabotegron seeks to use powerful\Nbombs known as "Mexican Flowers"
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.23,0:01:38.66,Narrator,,0,0,0,,to wreak destruction\Naround Japan.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.01,0:01:43.98,NEP AND TITLE,,0,0,0,,{\blur1\fs135\bord0\fnCienfuegos\4aFF\1c&HFCFFFE&\b1\pos(510.495,256.833)}Sabotegron Strikes Back
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.29,0:01:51.00,Default,,0,0,0,,There he is...\Nthe Kamen Rider...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.00,0:01:53.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Bloom, Mexican Flowers!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.82,0:02:22.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Rider!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.73,0:02:27.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Look out!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.85,0:03:13.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Rider Power!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.48,0:03:31.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Rider!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.35,0:03:33.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Rider Jump!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.04,0:03:43.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Rider Kick!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.84,0:03:49.38,Default,,0,0,0,,The cactus monster is gone...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.38,0:03:50.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Is that the end of it?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.71,0:03:52.94,Default,,0,0,0,,No, Sabotegron isn't dead.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.94,0:03:56.81,Default,,0,0,0,,I can hear him fleeing\Ndeep into the earth.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.02,0:04:04.54,Default,,0,0,0,,That's right... the Kamen Rider's hearing\Nis over ten times better than ours, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.98,0:04:08.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Mr. Tachibana. Taki.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.72,0:04:10.57,Default,,0,0,0,,As long as Sabotegron lives...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.57,0:04:13.47,Default,,0,0,0,,No, as long as Shocker continues\Nto seek world domination,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.47,0:04:15.37,Default,,0,0,0,,will you work with me?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.81,0:04:16.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Of course!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.63,0:04:17.50,Default,,0,0,0,,You bet!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.50,0:04:18.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.48,0:04:24.27,Default,,0,0,0,,I will slaughter all\Nthree of them together!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.27,0:04:26.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Just you wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.23,0:04:36.92,Narrator Bottom,,0,0,0,,Name: Ichimonji Hayato.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.78,0:04:44.60,Narrator Bottom,,0,0,0,,Special skills:\NSuperior athleticism.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.60,0:04:48.89,Narrator Bottom,,0,0,0,,Sixth degree black belt in\Njudo, fifth in karate.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.52,0:04:53.17,Narrator Bottom,,0,0,0,,We will turn this\Nman into a cyborg
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.17,0:04:56.13,Narrator Bottom,,0,0,0,,and send him to\Nfight Kamen Rider.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.25,0:05:03.78,Narrator Bottom,,0,0,0,,Stop this! Don't do this!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.17,0:05:09.16,Default,,0,0,0,,That's no good.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.32,0:05:15.94,Default,,0,0,0,,I thought I'd given up on being\Nanything but a cyborg now...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.40,0:05:21.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Time to get it together,\NIchimonji Hayato!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.96,0:05:26.35,Default,,0,0,0,,I was altered to\Nfight the Kamen Rider.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.50,0:05:32.76,Default,,0,0,0,,But the Hongo Rider saved me,\Nand now I'm the Kamen Rider.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.82,0:05:38.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Shocker must be so\Ndisappointed in me!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.74,0:05:49.40,Default,,0,0,0,,What are you doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.36,0:05:54.24,Default,,0,0,0,,What brings you here this\Nearly in the morning?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.23,0:05:57.34,Default,,0,0,0,,And how did you know I was here?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.34,0:06:00.62,Default,,0,0,0,,I've got a mysterious\Nsense for these things.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.62,0:06:03.29,Default,,0,0,0,,For instance,\Nsay I notice my cat's gone missing.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.29,0:06:08.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Then in a flash, I can tell\N"Oh, it's under my bed!"
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.89,0:06:12.43,Default,,0,0,0,,So I'm a cat,\Nas far as you're concerned?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.85,0:06:14.31,Default,,0,0,0,,So, what did you want?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.31,0:06:15.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, right.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.36,0:06:17.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Please, won't you photograph me?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.37,0:06:20.01,Default,,0,0,0,,I already told you, no.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.01,0:06:21.73,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't photograph women.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.73,0:06:23.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you sure?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.34,0:06:27.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Most men would trip over themselves\Nto snap a pretty girl like me.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.03,0:06:28.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Look, the door is this way.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.72,0:06:31.47,Default,,0,0,0,,I haven't given up, okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.00,0:06:33.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, you forget this.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.92,0:06:36.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, but that isn't mine.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.12,0:06:37.63,Default,,0,0,0,,It was in front of your\Ndoor when I arrived.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.63,0:06:38.99,Default,,0,0,0,,In front of my door?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.69,0:06:41.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Open it, why don't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.99,0:06:42.86,Default,,0,0,0,,But it's mine.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.86,0:06:44.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't be such a square!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.79,0:06:46.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Fine, I'll open it.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.09,0:06:50.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Just don't blame me if it\Nliterally blows up in our faces.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.72,0:06:52.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, how thrilling!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.83,0:06:54.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Thrilling?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.22,0:07:06.50,Default,,0,0,0,,A Mexican Flower...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.50,0:07:08.32,Default,,0,0,0,,It's beautiful!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.32,0:07:09.76,Default,,0,0,0,,I wish it was for me!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.76,0:07:09.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Stop.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.91,0:07:11.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't move.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.72,0:07:12.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Why not?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.53,0:07:15.76,Default,,0,0,0,,If you touch its\Nthorns, you'll die.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.28,0:07:18.58,Default,,0,0,0,,How do you know?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.64,0:07:24.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Get down!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.38,0:07:31.24,Default,,0,0,0,,See?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.32,0:07:35.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Where was it again?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.12,0:07:36.18,Default,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.18,0:07:38.37,Default,,0,0,0,,I saw another package\Njust like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.37,0:07:39.41,Default,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.01,0:07:41.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Where was it? Try to remember!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.39,0:07:44.24,Default,,0,0,0,,It's harder to remember\Nwhen you yell at me!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.24,0:07:47.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Please. I'll photograph you, even.\NJust try to remember!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.49,0:07:49.59,Default,,0,0,0,,I know! The club...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.06,0:07:52.20,Default,,0,0,0,,On the counter at\Nthe Racing Club!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.57,0:07:54.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Mr. Tachibana's store...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.19,0:07:56.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Damn you, you Shocker cowards!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.19,0:08:02.48,Sign,,0,0,0,,{\fs60\c&HD02946&\3c&HDBE6DC&}Tachibana Auto Corner
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.46,0:08:05.07,Default,,0,0,0,,What's in it?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.07,0:08:06.79,Default,,0,0,0,,We get to open it and find out.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.62,0:08:10.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, it's a cactus!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.95,0:08:13.73,Default,,0,0,0,,What a fashionable present...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.25,0:08:16.35,Default,,0,0,0,,I didn't know the chairman\Nhad such good taste...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.20,0:08:19.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Shiro,\Nwhy don't you wake up the boss?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.60,0:08:22.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Michi's been waiting\Nfor him to time her.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.24,0:08:24.15,Default,,0,0,0,,I want to learn how to\Nride, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.60,0:08:28.38,Default,,0,0,0,,This is a heck of a racing\Nclub, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.38,0:08:31.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Nobody in it knows how to ride!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.81,0:08:34.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Stop grumbling.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.22,0:08:35.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Now, hurry!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.51,0:08:36.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Hurry!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.64,0:08:37.88,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.88,0:08:40.02,Default,,0,0,0,,I haven't shown it\Nto the chairman yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.02,0:08:41.58,Default,,0,0,0,,But it's just a cactus!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.26,0:08:47.00,Default,,0,0,0,,That was a close call...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.55,0:08:55.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Too damned early for all this noise...\Nwhat's up?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.01,0:08:57.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Mr. Tachibana,\Nhere's the source of the noise.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.57,0:09:03.22,Default,,0,0,0,,A Mexican Flower.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.22,0:09:07.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Th-That's a cactus bomb!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.74,0:09:08.74,Default,,0,0,0,,A bomb?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.76,0:09:11.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Who brought this here?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.97,0:09:17.02,Default,,0,0,0,,It was that man!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.02,0:09:18.83,Default,,0,0,0,,He was watching to see\Nif it would explode...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.58,0:09:18.83,Default,,0,0,0,,All right...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.43,0:09:20.70,Default,,0,0,0,,He'll pay!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.70,0:09:22.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Come on, let's show him!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.36,0:09:23.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, girls!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.35,0:09:33.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Hold it!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.03,0:09:50.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.93,0:09:52.23,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm fine...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.14,0:10:17.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Take this!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.20,0:10:19.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Michi! You okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.18,0:10:20.18,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm fine!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.32,0:10:39.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Someone help! Help!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.92,0:10:42.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Transform.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.35,0:11:08.75,Default,,0,0,0,,I see... I'd heard Shocker\Nwas cruel and callous,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.75,0:11:10.83,Default,,0,0,0,,but I see you'll\Neven kill women...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.91,0:11:13.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Run!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.53,0:11:14.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.49,0:11:39.45,Default,,0,0,0,,All right... where can I find\Nyour commander, Sabotegron?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.75,0:11:54.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Let this be a lesson not\Nto charge off blindly.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.34,0:11:58.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.44,0:12:06.33,Bumper Episode 14-51,,0,0,0,,{\blur1\fs85\pos(311,454)}KAMEN RIDER
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.18,0:12:09.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, say something!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.46,0:12:11.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Stop it, Shiro.\NHe's not talking.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.82,0:12:13.97,Default,,0,0,0,,But it's just so frustrating!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.97,0:12:16.50,Default,,0,0,0,,We got ourselves a hostage,\Nbut he won't even make a peep!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.99,0:12:20.05,Default,,0,0,0,,According to Hayato...\NI mean, the Kamen Rider,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.05,0:12:22.78,Default,,0,0,0,,he's a cyborg\Nspecialized for combat.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.02,0:12:25.92,Default,,0,0,0,,A cyborg specialized for combat?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.89,0:12:29.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, they're probably\Ndesigned to be mute,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.73,0:12:32.28,Default,,0,0,0,,just in case they\Nfall into enemy hands.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.28,0:12:33.93,Default,,0,0,0,,That's so creepy!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.93,0:12:35.77,Default,,0,0,0,,If Shocker conquers the world,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.77,0:12:38.98,Default,,0,0,0,,you think they'll do the\Nsame thing to everyone?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.98,0:12:41.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Well,\Ngiven how worthless you are,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.76,0:12:43.76,Default,,0,0,0,,you'll be a cyborg specialized\Nfor mopping floors.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.32,0:12:46.83,Default,,0,0,0,,That's a mean joke to make.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.35,0:12:50.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's see...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.33,0:12:52.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Chairman.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.65,0:12:54.80,Default,,0,0,0,,You're not going out, are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.80,0:12:56.24,Default,,0,0,0,,You can't leave me\Nalone with this guy!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.24,0:12:57.83,Default,,0,0,0,,I am, and I can!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.49,0:13:00.36,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm going to drop in on Hayato.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.36,0:13:02.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't worry!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.83,0:13:04.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Keep watch a while.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.12,0:13:05.48,Default,,0,0,0,,But, Chairman...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.36,0:13:12.30,Default,,0,0,0,,I hope they know\Nwhat they're doing,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.30,0:13:15.26,Default,,0,0,0,,leaving a precious hostage\Nunguarded like this...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.89,0:13:17.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't blame me if\Nsomething goes wrong!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.39,0:13:26.72,Default,,0,0,0,,They're here... they're here!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.45,0:13:31.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, God, they're going to\Nmake me a janitor cyborg!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.12,0:13:33.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Please, spare me!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.52,0:13:38.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, what's your problem?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.63,0:13:40.01,Default,,0,0,0,,I think he's trembling!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.00,0:13:45.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't scare me like that!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.09,0:13:47.44,Default,,0,0,0,,What are you doing here?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.44,0:13:49.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Look, Yuri!\NIt's the bad guy hostage!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.24,0:13:55.29,Default,,0,0,0,,That's quite a face\Nhe's got on him...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.13,0:14:00.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Is he the one you two caught?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.94,0:14:03.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Something like that...\Nright, Michi?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.93,0:14:06.43,Default,,0,0,0,,What a shame...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.43,0:14:08.25,Default,,0,0,0,,I wish I'd gone along.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.83,0:14:11.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, Shiro.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.20,0:14:12.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Why don't we help\Nyou keep watch?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.14,0:14:14.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank goodness!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.71,0:14:17.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Even girls like you are\Nbetter than nothing...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.81,0:14:18.50,Default,,0,0,0,,What's that?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.50,0:14:20.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, nothing!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.91,0:14:25.63,Default,,0,0,0,,It really is a creepy face...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.63,0:14:27.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Definitely not an\N"in" look at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.68,0:14:32.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Wow, they're not even scared...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.16,0:14:35.60,Default,,0,0,0,,What goes on in\Nthese girls' heads?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.70,0:14:37.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Ow!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.85,0:14:41.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Look! There's a cactus thorn\Nsticking out of the floor!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.72,0:14:51.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Murderer!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.81,0:14:54.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Bring it on!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.52,0:15:00.95,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm scared!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.25,0:15:02.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Mommy!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.86,0:15:13.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Incompetent fool!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.50,0:15:15.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Normally I'd kill you for this,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.81,0:15:19.55,Default,,0,0,0,,but we need every combatant\Nwe can get for Operation: Z.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.55,0:15:21.42,Default,,0,0,0,,So I'll overlook your\Nfailure just this once.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.42,0:15:22.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Understood?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.64,0:15:24.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Now, come along!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.11,0:15:51.86,Default,,0,0,0,,I need to see your permit.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.18,0:16:25.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Security's pretty tight, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.61,0:16:29.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Shocker's base must be\Nunder that statue...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.40,0:16:30.44,Default,,0,0,0,,All right...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.68,0:16:47.82,Default,,0,0,0,,That was a close one.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.02,0:16:49.62,Default,,0,0,0,,One more step and I'd\Nhave been roasted.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.15,0:16:51.67,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll have to take\Nthe long way around.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.24,0:17:48.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Sorry about this.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.01,0:18:09.41,Default,,0,0,0,,This is some outpost\Nthey've got...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.57,0:18:18.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Gentlemen.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.92,0:18:23.20,Default,,0,0,0,,I will now explain\NShocker's Operation: Z.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.65,0:18:29.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Operation: Z, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.73,0:18:31.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's hear all about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.90,0:18:35.69,Default,,0,0,0,,The total destruction of\Nthe prominent Sakuma Dam...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.69,0:18:38.60,Default,,0,0,0,,This is Operation: Z.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.60,0:18:41.60,Default,,0,0,0,,First, let's have a\Nlook at the Sakuma Dam.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.42,0:18:50.95,Default,,0,0,0,,If the Sakuma Dam is destroyed,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.95,0:18:54.07,Default,,0,0,0,,it will paralyze the city of\NTenryu, which lies downstream.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.19,0:19:00.50,Default,,0,0,0,,In the ensuing chaos,\NShocker's forces will occupy Tenryu.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.50,0:19:04.75,Default,,0,0,0,,We'll make this a bridgehead\Nfor Shocker in Japan,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.75,0:19:08.71,Default,,0,0,0,,so that our reach can spread to\Nencompass the entire country.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.71,0:19:09.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Commander.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.73,0:19:12.63,Default,,0,0,0,,What weapons will we\Nuse in the destruction?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.74,0:19:16.94,Default,,0,0,0,,The Mexican Flowers I brought\Nfrom Mexico, of course.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.52,0:19:18.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait a minute.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.84,0:19:21.48,Default,,0,0,0,,What's a guard like you doing\Nhere in the operations division?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.67,0:19:25.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Guess I put on the\Nwrong uniform...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.29,0:19:26.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Take off your mask!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.97,0:19:29.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Damn...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.24,0:19:32.15,Default,,0,0,0,,I didn't realize you had different\Nuniforms for different divisions!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.42,0:19:36.04,Default,,0,0,0,,FBI scum... catch him!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.43,0:19:42.12,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll kill you!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.79,0:19:44.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.72,0:19:46.68,Default,,0,0,0,,We can always kill him later.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.68,0:19:51.23,Default,,0,0,0,,For now, use him as bait to\Nlure out the Kamen Rider.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.85,0:19:55.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Use this man...\Nto lure out the Kamen Rider?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.04,0:19:58.90,Default,,0,0,0,,And if I arrange the destruction\Nof the dam in the meantime...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.90,0:20:00.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Good.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.34,0:20:01.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Take him to the dungeon!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.95,0:20:23.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Rider!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.26,0:20:26.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Taki, the storehouse for\Nthe Mexican Flower bombs
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.37,0:20:28.78,Default,,0,0,0,,lies beyond that wall.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.83,0:20:32.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Stand back.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.51,0:20:39.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Hurry!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.83,0:21:04.93,Default,,0,0,0,,One more!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.44,0:21:23.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Sabotegron!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.26,0:21:33.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Rider!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.13,0:21:34.97,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll take these guys.\NYou handle that monster!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.82,0:21:44.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Kamen Rider. I will not flee!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.93,0:21:46.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Come to me! This way!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.26,0:21:51.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Show yourself, Sabotegron!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.25,0:21:54.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Rider!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.55,0:21:59.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Your interference with\Nmy plans here in Japan
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.93,0:22:02.07,Default,,0,0,0,,has tarnished the golden\Nreputation I earned in Mexico.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.07,0:22:03.20,Default,,0,0,0,,I am going to die...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.20,0:22:05.31,Default,,0,0,0,,But I won't go alone.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.31,0:22:08.91,Default,,0,0,0,,So that the name of Sabotegron can live\Non in glory in the halls of Shocker,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:08.91,0:22:10.27,Default,,0,0,0,,I will take you with me!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.06,0:22:13.61,Default,,0,0,0,,My life won't be lost\Nto a Shocker commander
Dialogue: 0,0:22:13.61,0:22:15.89,Default,,0,0,0,,who sold his soul and\Nhis body to devils!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:16.65,0:22:19.14,Default,,0,0,0,,I won't let you\Nleave the arsenal!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:43.19,0:22:45.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Rider Jump!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:01.71,0:23:03.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Rider!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:11.29,0:23:12.39,Default,,0,0,0,,That's right...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:12.39,0:23:14.27,Default,,0,0,0,,He's an invincible cyborg!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:25.51,0:23:28.00,Narrator,,0,0,0,,The Kamen Rider beat\Nthe monstrous Sabotegron,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:28.00,0:23:29.89,Narrator,,0,0,0,,who had come to\NJapan from Mexico.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:29.89,0:23:34.85,Narrator,,0,0,0,,But Shocker would sharpen its claws in\Npreparation for its next opportunity.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:38.16,0:23:40.69,Cont,,0,0,0,,{\blur.8\fad(0,400)}To be continued
Dialogue: 0,0:23:41.10,0:23:43.51,NEP AND TITLE,,0,0,0,,{\blur1\4aFF\bord0\b1\fs67.5\fnCalibri\pos(499.031,496.481)}Next Episode Preview
Dialogue: 0,0:23:41.10,0:23:45.20,Narrator,,0,0,0,,The next assassin sent by Shocker\NHQ to kill our Kamen Rider
Dialogue: 0,0:23:45.20,0:23:46.47,Narrator,,0,0,0,,is Pirasaurus.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:46.47,0:23:49.89,Narrator,,0,0,0,,The mighty pro wrestler Kusaka Noboru\Nis transformed into Pirasaurus,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:49.89,0:23:51.61,Narrator,,0,0,0,,who is controlled by the\Nfemale Shocker commander Maya.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:51.61,0:23:55.95,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Kamen Rider ends up in a series\Nof clashes against Pirasaurus.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:56.30,0:24:00.15,Narrator Bottom,,0,0,0,,Join us next week for "The\NDevil Wrestler, Pirasaurus."
Dialogue: 0,0:23:56.10,0:24:01.06,NEP AND TITLE,,0,0,0,,{\fscx100\fs155\bord0\fnCienfuegos\4aFF\b1\pos(717.167,425.389)}Pirasaurus
Dialogue: 0,0:23:56.10,0:24:01.06,NEP AND TITLE,,0,0,0,,{\fscx100\fs135\bord0\fnCienfuegos\4aFF\b1\pos(377.167,170.389)}The Devil Wrestler
Dialogue: 0,0:24:02.79,0:24:09.63,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,He came here on a storm...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:10.14,0:24:12.22,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,Who is he? Who is he?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:12.22,0:24:14.18,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,Who is this man of storms,
Dialogue: 0,0:24:14.18,0:24:17.22,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,who sends the\Nvillains scattering?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:17.72,0:24:19.60,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,Kamen Rider!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:19.60,0:24:21.48,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,His mask stands for justice!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:21.48,0:24:23.27,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,Start it up! Rev it up!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:23.27,0:24:24.61,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,Get that engine running!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:25.07,0:24:27.11,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,Give me top speed, Cyclone!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:29.15,0:24:32.82,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,Hit them with\Nall of your anger!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:32.82,0:24:36.41,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,Put an end to Shocker's evil!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:36.41,0:24:40.00,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,Rider! Rider!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:40.50,0:24:44.25,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,Kamen Rider!